---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="My Portfolio">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
        
        <header class="mb-20">
            <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl text-white">
                Hi, I'm <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Your Name</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400">
                I'm a passionate web developer who loves building fast, beautiful, and accessible websites. Welcome to my corner of the internet.
            </p>
        </header>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Featured Projects</h2>
            <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
                
                <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-6 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/10">
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">Project One</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-400">A brief description of what this project does and the tech stack used to build it.</p>
                    <a href="/project-one" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">
                        View Project 
                        <span class="ml-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">&rarr;</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-6 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/10">
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">Abaki - AI Repository Monitor</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-400">.NET 8 REST API with AI-powered code auto-fixing, GitHub integration, and real-time updates.</p>
                    <a href="/abaki-overview" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">
                        View Project 
                        <span class="ml-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">&rarr;</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-6 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/10">
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">SYP Sozialkaufhaus</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-400">Spring Boot 3.4.5 backend for an online auction platform with real-time bidding and email integration.</p>
                    <a href="/syp-overview" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">
                        View Project 
                        <span class="ml-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">&rarr;</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Abaki Deep Dives</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-400">The Abaki project is complex and multi-faceted. Here are focused explorations of its core components:</p>
            <div class="grid gap-4">
                <a href="/abaki-auth" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">1. User Authentication & JWT Security</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Secure registration, BCrypt password hashing, and JWT token generation</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/abaki-github" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">2. GitHub Repository Integration</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Octokit integration, webhook management, and repository monitoring</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/abaki-autofix" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">3. AI-Powered Code Auto-Fix Engine</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Async streaming HTTP client, real-time token processing, and AI integration</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/abaki-database" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">4. Database & Entity Framework Architecture</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Relational schema design, migrations, and query optimization</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/abaki-encryption" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">5. API Key Management & Encryption</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">AES-256 encryption, secure token storage, and key rotation</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/abaki-logging" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">6. Activity Logging & Real-time SignalR Hub</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Structured logging with Serilog, file rotation, and WebSocket communication</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-white">SYP Sozialkaufhaus Deep Dives</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-400">A Spring Boot 3.4.5 backend for an online auction platform. Here are the core components I built:</p>
            <div class="grid gap-4">
                <a href="/syp-springboot-setup" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">1. Spring Boot Setup & Multi-Profile Configuration</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Maven, environment profiles, and secrets management</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/syp-service-layer" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">2. Service Layer Architecture</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Item and Sponsor services with pagination, validation, and business logic</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/syp-email-integration" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">3. Email Integration with Local Testing</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Spring Mail, async email, and Papercut/Mailtrap integration</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/syp-logging-strategy" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">4. Structured Logging with Log4j2</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">File rotation, async appenders, and production-ready observability</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/syp-integration-testing" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">5. Integration Testing with JUnit & Spring Boot Test</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Unit tests with Mockito, integration tests, and test fixtures</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/syp-load-testing" class="group block rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-4 transition-all hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-300">6. Load Testing with Artillery</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Performance testing, realistic scenarios, and bottleneck identification</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Skills & Tools</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                {['Astro', 'Tailwind CSS', 'JavaScript', 'TypeScript', 'HTML', 'Git', 'C#', '.NET 8', 'Entity Framework Core', 'SQLite', 'REST APIs', 'SignalR', 'JWT', 'Encryption', 'Java 17', 'Spring Boot', 'JPA/Hibernate', 'MS SQL Server', 'Maven', 'Log4j2', 'JUnit 5', 'Mockito', 'Artillery'].map((skill) => (
                    <span class="rounded-full border border-gray-700 bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:text-white">
                        {skill}
                    </span>
                ))}
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Let's Connect</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-400">I'm always open to discussing new projects, creative ideas, or opportunities.</p>
            <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-all hover:bg-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-950">
                Say Hello
            </a>
        </section>

    </main>
</Layout>